name: MachineLearningPaperFetcher
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: machine learning paper fetcher
des:
This skill will make sure you stay updated on the research being done in machine learning. This skill will list the titles and authors of new machine learning papers published every day. Just open this skill and ask it to catch you up.

Updates you can expect in the future:
1. If you don't have time to listen to the paper names and authors, get them in your inbox through email.
2. And yes, a better icon.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
